Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR性能试验 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过部分改装也只有这种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来您不太满意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哪台机体让我满意过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有耐心等待新机体完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为提高响应速度 正在最后调试阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这台机体 新型高达也不足为俱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加紧完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拟定了以我为主抗击高达的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我 从没有惧怕过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.73,0:02:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达孜 XRounder们的冰眠结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 据报刚才已经全部苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西尔哥哥 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 德西尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜伏任务归来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻您的冰眠结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此赶来报告哥哥一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 潜伏任务一定够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样高水平的XRounder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小享有高度自由的权限 活跃在前线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会像你这样被派去杂用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而还会受到保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特看人从不走眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特司令官 可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 各部队作战准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被任命为地球占领军司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时哥哥在冰眠中…故未能及时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 你爬到我的头上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计抵达作战宇域前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体将会调试完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和我说预计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作战意义重大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断进化的机动战士 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构成其中枢的AGE系统 就是我们的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据情报 AGE系统的核心部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就置于高达胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上随时收集需要的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 这次的目标是AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取也好 破坏也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 难免与高达一战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 竟然有这样的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的技术水准完全出乎我们预料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦至今未能解密AGE系统的内部程序
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于无法拷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要控制它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以阻止高达进一步进化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是高达母舰的预测航线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们中途埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 如果去往联邦总司令部BIG RING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最短的路径…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XD37 岩礁宇域…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号 即将驶入XD37岩礁宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员进入多障碍区域航行态势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么那么没骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想 索敌系统的性能发挥会受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能不被维甘发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是变更航线的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下要尽可能避免战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗…能避开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽 在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是在担心那家伙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不！ 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 新兵蛋子 吃得惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是嚼完了咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让它变成打仗时的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和正常吃有什么区别？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么区别 有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃的时候使劲吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别等饿了后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 敌人什么时候来都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调试已经全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会让我满意吗 Zeydra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zeydra是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为发挥XRounder实力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门研发的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击时请记得戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是控制杰哈特大人XRounder能力的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更准确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有助于能力的稳定发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和机体实现沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就杰哈特大人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果最大限度发挥能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体本身会支撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有力量的不便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短时间内反复佩卸无法发挥其性能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期征战时请平日就戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 红得就像个靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看 司令官大人的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在说服不了自己和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你愁眉苦脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话跟我说吧 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次出战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想过敌人机师的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没那种闲工夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有工夫也不会去想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人屁股就是被用来打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们家的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员战斗配置 全员战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对照索敌数据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各应急班站点就位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在这条路径上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 保养完了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是老爸 是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 要叫我中尉 说了多少遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 保养完没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…没问题 亚瑟姆的AGE2也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克中尉GJ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唠唠叨叨又要被妈妈说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克先生是你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都说我像妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统对照完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dorado 6机 Baqto 2机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这种地方进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 新兵蛋子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩礁宇域的战斗 对你们来说还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敌人来了就没有不迎接的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别因为上次的事畏畏缩缩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻就该有点冲劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 沃尔夫队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆·明日野 高达AGE2 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队 出击完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对维甘机动战士部队 采取迎击态势…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B543反应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机后方又出现疑似维甘机体1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在以三倍速度接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 你是我的对手吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机后方B543 出现疑似维甘机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向沃尔夫队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他机体的三倍速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩礁宇域里这种速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 保佑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的们 客人不是只有一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先试试手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也行 就像上次那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一架架来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静 镇静 镇静 镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明机种 闯入机动战士队战斗宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我来会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 先打下一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 它奔你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台机体能跟上我的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度吗 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新型机的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得也挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特 麦克斯 阿莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂兵交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是杂兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎 我们俩一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 一对一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的对手是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一台在攻击高达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他根本不做理睬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特！ 是杰哈特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 是杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是对手又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫我是又如何 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想战斗的话 就从战场上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连撤退的觉悟也没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来此的目的就是击落高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你当作朋友 是我的一厢情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是 这么好欺负的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度就敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前撒野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来就来 给你个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有冲劲是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了什么都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 XRounder的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以不适合战斗 不只是因为天真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说 司令官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让高达给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹩脚的谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放水饶了朋友一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想骗过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊泽尔坎特大人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己关在房间里 看来该教训下他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人 有时候会需要一个人静下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特 是故意放过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.47,0:22:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说 我没有上战场的实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也！
